    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/atul_gawande_527230",
        "quote": "Every country in the world is battling the rising cost of health care. No community anywhere has demonstrably lowered its health-care costs (not just slowed their rate of increase) by improving medical services. They've lowered costs only by cutting or rationing them.",
