            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/atul_gawande_527222",
        "quote": "I think we are faced in medicine with the reality that we have to be willing to talk about our failures and think hard about them, even despite the malpractice system. I mean, there are things that we can do to make that system better.",
