                "url": "/topics/george_orwell"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/atul_gawande_527227",
        "quote": "No one looks at your hands to see how much they shake when you are interviewed to be a surgeon. The physical skills required are no greater than for writing cursive script. If an operation requires so much skill only a few surgeons can do it, you modify the operation to make it simpler.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Atul Gawande",
