                "name": "Shake",
                "url": "/topics/shake"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/atul_gawande_527229",
        "quote": "If I get hit by a bus tomorrow, my patients will not even be postponed. Another surgeon would step in and take over. The reason to do research and writing is that it at least makes me feel not entirely replaceable. If I didn't write, I don't know if I would do surgery.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Atul Gawande",
            "url": "/quotes/atul_gawande_527229"
